article_title: Addressing the hidden side of Fairfax County
article_text:
Reston, VA (20191)

Today

Partly cloudy.

Tonight

Mostly cloudy skies this evening will become partly cloudy after midnight. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. Low near 65F. SSW winds at 10 to 15 mph, decreasing to less than 5 mph.

article_metadata.author:
Angela Woolsey
Fairfax County Times

og.description: Two Virginia legislators called on Virginia to join other states in expanding Medicaid at a Sept. 15 event hosted by the nonprofit Medical Care for Children Partnership (MCCP) Foundation.
